The site is basically like a facebook but it will only work in gla because for making account each one needs it “@gla.ac.in” email id . Connecting all Glaians inside the university can make them to proper communication between them and each one can know each other better than before .
BEst idea for local communication.

GOALS
To connect all Glaians to each other through a better way .
Easy to manage club and society events and do invitation.
Promotion to Indian digitalization.
To give departments autonomy over their social media.
Supporting university recruitment efforts.
Engendering pride in the university among students, faculty, staff and alumni.
Engaging parents with the university.
Accelerating the sense of belonging for incoming students.
Helping alumni feel connected to their alma master .
Sharing accurate university information in real time.
Support digital india
have fun with friends.

